Smart DMS processes user-provided documents, OCR output, AI provider responses,
email content, metadata and configuration values. OCR results and AI-extracted
metadata can be incomplete or incorrect. Users are responsible for validating
important data, protecting secrets, keeping backups and testing restore
procedures before relying on Smart DMS for important documents.

